column5: I'm just wondering if there's a place on the way to morson entering Canada at rainy river to buy Cuban cigars and leeches or do I need to drive across at Fort Frances.
I find that to be rare combination since Buck and Ernestos closed.
Buena Vista carries leeches. I have no idea about cuban cigars.
Thanks Jared. I did find the cigars close to home.
It's been years since I've been in Rainy River Ont. but I think you can get Cuban cigars at the duty free shop or at the town grocery store. Sorry, I can't help you with livebait.
